      "background": "../assets/cg/rescue_event.png?v=20260701",
      "characters": [],
      "speaker": "ガリュ㌧",
      "hideName": true,
      "text": "「……その夜は、冷たい雨が石畳を打ちつけておった。」",
      "se": null,
      "choices": null
    },
    {
      "id": "rain-rescue-07",
      "background": "../assets/cg/rescue_event.png?v=20260701",
      "characters": [],
      "speaker": "ガリュ㌧",
      "hideName": true,
      "text": "「まるで天が涙を流しておるかのようにな。」",
      "se": null,
      "choices": null
    },
    {
      "id": "rain-rescue-08",
      "background": "../assets/cg/rescue_event.png?v=20260701",
      "characters": [],
      "speaker": "ガリュ㌧",
      "hideName": true,
      "text": "「巡幸の馬車が通りかかり、王と妃が見つけたのは、雨の中で倒れていた年端もいかぬ少年じゃった。」",
      "se": null,
      "choices": null
    },
    {
      "id": "rain-rescue-09",
      "background": "../assets/cg/rescue_event.png?v=20260701",
      "characters": [],
      "speaker": "ガリュ㌧",
      "hideName": true,
      "text": "「これが、すべての始まりであった。」",
      "nextSceneId": "castle-morning-01",
      "se": null,
      "choices": null
    },
    {
      "id": "castle-morning-01",
      "scene": "castle-morning",
      "background": "../assets/bg/castle_outside.png?v=20260701",
      "characters": [],
      "speaker": "ガリュ㌧",
      "hideName": true,
      "text": "「その日、王国はいつもと変わらぬ朝を迎えておった。」",
      "se": null,
      "choices": null
    },
    {
      "id": "castle-morning-02",
      "scene": "castle-morning",
      "background": "../assets/bg/castle_outside.png?v=20260701",
      "characters": [],
      "speaker": "ガリュ㌧",
      "hideName": true,
      "text": "「誰もまだ、この国の運命が大きく動き始めることを知らなかった。」",
      "autoAdvanceMs": 3000,
      "nextSceneId": "scene3",
      "se": null,
      "choices": null
    },
    {
